A man is walking nervously along the corridor of the hospital, near the operating room. After three hours of waiting, the surgeon comes out of the operating room and with a mournful expression on his face, says to the man:
- I have some bad news for you. At the third hour of the operation, your mother...
the man interrupts:
- It's not my mother! This is my mother-in-law!
The surgeon's face gathers joy and he says:
- I have good news for you. At the third hour of the operation...
